that it is to pray
for Grandmother's blessing.

42
00:02:14,160 --> 00:02:15,560
Su Qingran,

43
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,230
you wretched woman.

44
00:02:17,720 --> 00:02:19,350
You actually want to drive me away.

45
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:20,950
Concubine Gong,

46
00:02:21,600 --> 00:02:24,040
