Bring her up.

54
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,720
Miss, she's here.

55
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:50,510
Aren't you He Tao,
Gong Xi's maidservant?

56
00:02:50,880 --> 00:02:53,440
You fell into a well and died back then.

57
00:02:53,630 --> 00:02:56,070
How are you still alive?

58
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,720
Master, Madam Dowager, Lady Qingran.

59
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:04,230
Lady Qingran.

60
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,600
Lady Qingran,

61
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,750
