62
00:03:10,220 --> 00:03:12,280
Is it true Concubine Gong
caused my mother's death?

63
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,350
Yeah.

64
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:20,510
Back then, I saw with my own eyes
how she poisoned Madam,

65
00:03:20,560 --> 00:03:24,510
and pushed Madam Dowager into the water
to blame it on Lady Qingran.

66
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:29,400
I wanted to tell Madam Dowager
the truth.

67
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,560
But Concubine Gong found it out.

68
00:03:31,950 --> 00:03:33,670
She pushed me into the well.

69
00:03:34,070 --> 00:03:35,470
Fortunately, I survived.

70
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:38,670
All these years, in order to keep her
from finding me,

71
00:03:38,950 --> 00:03:40,720
I've been living under a false identity.

72
00:03:42,440 --> 00:03:43,440
Concubine Gong,

73
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,560
