but always blocked me.

78
00:03:58,750 --> 00:04:00,630
She claimed it was for my own good.

79
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:03,790
In truth, she couldn't bear
to see me well.

80
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,040
She just wanted
to protect her superiority.

81
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,600
Since she was unkind first,

82
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:11,400
