this disgusting woman again.

101
00:05:12,350 --> 00:05:13,430
Stay far away from me.

102
00:05:14,330 --> 00:05:15,410
What are you trying to do?

103
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,640
Mother! Mother!

104
00:05:17,200 --> 00:05:18,160
