I spared you from drowning in a cage.
You should be grateful.

115
00:05:50,550 --> 00:05:51,840
Your worldly ties are severed.

116
00:05:52,550 --> 00:05:55,790
You will stay at Lianhua Nunnery

117
00:05:56,520 --> 00:05:58,080
