122
00:06:23,840 --> 00:06:26,550
Concubine Gong's romantic history
is really rich.

123
00:06:28,550 --> 00:06:29,910
You know everything.

124
00:06:30,330 --> 00:06:31,840
You can not only imitate handwriting,

125
00:06:32,230 --> 00:06:33,760
